outputs.output_descr:
1.	Business Case, Programme and Baseline Report
2.	Students groups established and trained (to act as facilitators for a healthy lifestyles network - and each "managing" five local community groups);
3.	Twenty local community based groups established and trained (to advocate for healthy lifestyles in the local communities);
4.	Monitoring (Health Watch) Reports by students groups produced (regular monthly basis);
5.	A Special Report produced (at end of project);
6	National Seminar undertaken (to disseminate results);
7.	Project M&E .
